snippet.title: Get Bubble Wrap on Steam!
snippet.description:
🔵 https://store.steampowered.com/app/2718700/Bubble_Wrap/
The most relaxing app ever! It's like normal bubble wrap, but you never run out, can customise it, and get confetti blasted over your screen!





Music by Kevin MacLeod
